high_descs: Move to the counter on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Move to the fridge behind and to the right of you.
Open the fridge and place the knife inside a cup.
Pick up the cup with the knife inside of it and close the door.
Move to the sink to the right of you.
Place the cup in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to counter to left of stove.
Pick up knife from counter.
Turn left, cross room, turn right, walk to refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, put knife in glass on refrigerator shelf.
Pick up glass with knife in it.
Turn right, turn left, cross room to the sink.
Put glass with knife in it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put knife, glass in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife that's behind the egg.
Turn around, walk across the room, and turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the knife in the glass that's on the shelf with the tomato.
Pick up the glass with the knife in it, and close the fridge door.
Turn right, walk across the room, and stop in front of the sink.
Place the glass in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put dirty dishes in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go back to the counter.
Pick up the knife from beside the bread.
Take the knife and turn around. Turn right to find the fridge.
Place the knife inside the fridge.
Take out a glass with the knife in it.
Hold the glass and turn to the right to go back to the sink.
Place the glass and knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife and glass to the sink.

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter in between the sink and stove.
Turn around and starting walking to the window, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the butter knife inside the glass that is in the fridge.
Remove the glass with the butter knife inside of it from the fridge, then close the door.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the sink.
Place the glass with the butter knife inside into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a knife inside of it in the sink.
